FT  12 FEB 93 / N&amp;P announces BES launch
NATIONAL &amp; Provincial Building Society yesterday announced the launch of a
Pounds 50m Business Expansion Scheme. It hopes to reduce its stock of
repossessed properties by renting them through assured tenancies.
This follows the announcement of a similar plan by Bristol &amp; West which
should take 800 repossessions off its balance sheet.
